===Konata, Yutaka, and Minami=== {{Infobox Single | | Name = Lucky Star Character Song Vol. 010 Mune Pettan Girls | Cover = | Artist = [[Aya Hirano]], [[Shizuka Hasegawa]], and [[Minori Chihara]] | from Album = | B-side = | Released = October 31, 2007 | Format = [[Maxi single|Maxi]] | Recorded = | Genre = [[Single (music)|Single]] | Length = | Label = [[Lantis (company)|Lantis]] | Writer = | Producer = | Certification = | Last single = | This single = | Next single = }} '''''Lucky Star Character Song Vol. 010 Mune Pettan Girls''''' is the tenth volume of the character song albums and was released on October 31, 2007. The CD's title loosely means ''Flat-Chested Girls'', and the title of the song "Minna de 5ji Pittan", is a play on the game ''[[Mojipittan]]''.
